Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.34,0:00:14.01,Default,,0,0,5,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.71,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you used to live.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.26,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I also lived here in Kamakura in my younger days.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.62,0:00:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you called back when you were in middle school? {she uses "obaachan" here but I can't think of a good way to render it in English. D:} {How's "ma'am?"}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.13,0:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We just stuck to using surnames, so I was Godai.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Godai?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.08,0:00:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Godai Kaoruko...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.12,0:00:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, the youngest ever winner of the National Karate Championships, Godai Kaoruko?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.46,0:00:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're remarkably well-informed, considering how long ago it was.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.29,0:00:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:51.99,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.20,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.66,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Precure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:00.24,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:03.21,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Now, all together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:05.71,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:08.72,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Let's make our flowers bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.31,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Within each of our chests,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:18.98,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,they begin to sprout
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:20.65,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,The seeds of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:21.93,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,are growing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:24.56,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,bit by bit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:25.23,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Red,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:25.85,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,white
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.15,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,and yellow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:29.90,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,It's because these blooming buds are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:31.36,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,all varied colors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.81,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,that they
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.99,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,shine so brightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:40.28,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,That smile that you've nurtured
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.79,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,with such care
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.49,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,will never wither
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.13,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:52.00,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Now, all together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.46,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.13,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Let's make our flowers bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:02.05,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,They're always right by our sides
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:02.88,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,So together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:06.68,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,let's make those pretty flowers of our heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:09.68,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,bloom even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.18,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.69,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Precure!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You lived around here?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.54,0:02:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We lived a little further up in the mountains, but I remember coming here to shop a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.52,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.69,0:02:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. My friends and I are just \Nhere to visit during the Bon Festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Afternoon!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Myoudouin Itsuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of Hanasaki's friends, then?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What of it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this is my childhood friend, Nakano Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Likewise...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be doing well, Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How goes your kendo training?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been training day in and day out to get ready for the tournament. {Added the 'and.'}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the time to go waltzing \Nabout with girls whenever I feel like it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha, I see the problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.14,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sweet. You've made me remember my first love.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first love?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.51,0:03:25.10,Titles,,0,0,175,,{\bord0\blur0.45\fad(486,0)}Grandpa was a Hottie{\i1}?!{\i0}\N\N\N\N\N\NCure Flower's First Love{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:25.10,Titles,,0,0,175,,{\c&H000000&\blur0.45\shad2\fad(486,0)\1a&HFF&\t(441,486,\1a&H00&)}Grandpa was a Hottie{\i1}?!{\i0}\N\N\N\N\N\NCure Flower's First Love{\i1}!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on any longer!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Erika, that's pathetic!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to think I keep myself in pretty good shape, {lit: "good at physical activity". Feel free to find a more accurate balance if you can think of one. D:} {Added the 'pretty' modifier, let's call it good.}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but just climbing these mountain paths is so boring!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how well Grandma's doing compared to you!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right! I get it!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.42,0:03:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, just what is your\N relationship with that Mitsuru kid?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.62,0:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My relationship? We're childhood friends, that's all.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell us a bit more than that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.41,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he was young, Mitsuru's always been\N obsessed by kendo and trained almost constantly.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always quiet and rather reserved.{It's funny, the Japanese for "quiet" as in the personality trait is literally just "adult-like". This is why Japan sucks :V}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.64,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.69,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But whenever I got into trouble, Mitsuru would always appear to save me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.00,0:04:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in junior high, Mitsuru always seemed to appear out of nowhere to help me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.36,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, once we'd decided we were going to move to Kibougahana,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank Mitsuru for all the kindness he'd shown me. {Removed 'before then' at the end of the line - not needed for English parsing.}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never managed to see him?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. {Extend the timing on this a little, please.}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems like a nice kid.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why he dislikes me so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.64,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not sure either.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't get it?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.64,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.15,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnPolo\fax0.15\blur0.65\xshad2\frz350.2\c&H060706&\fscx83\fscy83\4c&H878286&\pos(231,262)\b1}Hanasaki
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.30,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how quickly houses fall\N into decay when nobody's living there. {no-one -> nobody}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This house has a lot of memories for your family, right, Tsubomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I was born and raised here, after all!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, that hurt...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.40,0:06:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I recognize that hot guy!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.89,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that sure takes me back.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your first time seeing a photo of Sora?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.94,0:06:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's your grandpa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda strange, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I find myself in trouble,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.53,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,a guy who is the spitting image of \Nthis photo always comes to save me!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's all right, could you please tell us more about Grandpa? {Capitalized 'grandpa.'}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how you met, and when you first started going out!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old, old story.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.86,0:06:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It all began when I was doing some secluded training in the mountains to prepare myself for the tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.82,0:07:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always felt so lonely, sleeping there alone at night.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.42,0:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't take it any longer, so I decided to head back.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All around that little mountain hut, my \Nfavorite flower, lavender, was blooming.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.81,0:07:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to disturb your playing.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.39,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoy performing more when there's an audience.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, come in.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, um, right...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a moment. I'll get you some lavender tea. {Removed 'I have just the thing,' as this was WAY TOO MANY WORDS for such a short line (and according to Tiffany, is still close to what he actually says in moon, anyhow)}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You live in this mountain cottage all by yourself, Sora? {Original: "You mean to say you live in this little mountain cottage all by yourself, Sora?" I cut it down a bit because, again, too much :wordswordswords: for the timeframe, and she doesn't seem to be being that elaborate.}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.50,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nature has blessed this place well, and as such I'm able to live a self-sufficient lifestyle here.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.62,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lonely out here on your own?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But the trees, plants, and leaves \Nprovide me most excellent company. {Added comma after 'plants.'}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I do happen to have something rather special. {Removed 'now I think of it' and changed 'Ah' to 'Actually.' Did you pick this translation up again at line 130ish after a break? It seems like the same issue keeps cropping up with his dialogue and I've never seen it from you before.}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A music box I made.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If ever you should feel lonely, then just listen to its melody. {Removed apostrophe from 'its.' You don't want 'it is' in there.}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.44,0:09:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was how I met Sora,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and how I found my first love.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beautiful!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that, you went on to \Nwin the karate championships?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.92,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to continue my training, thanks to that music box.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.17,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After winning, I went on to study\N botany with the same enthusiasm,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and I became closer and closer to Sora.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened then?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We got married.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.66,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, after Youichi was born, Sora made a promise to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to grow a beautiful field of\N lavender on this mountainside, just for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.59,0:10:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's finished, will you listen to me play my cello again, amongst the lavender?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.82,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora went up to Heaven and left me here alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.04,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you never found out where the lavender field was?{Literally "what happened to it", but LATER CONTEXT etc.}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.54,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually Youichi got married,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were born.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so strange.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.02,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown so old, and yet, in my mind, \NSora is still the same as he was back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.11,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose because he passed on so early, I \Nstill think of him as he was when we first met.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Grandpa's?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.94,0:11:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last memento of his I have left.{'of his left' -> 'left of his'}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What about the music box?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.08,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.54,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.31,0:11:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved that music box so much and always listened to it,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so Grandma gave it to me as a present,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.34,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but when we moved, it vanished from my luggage.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Grandma...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already forgiven you, you silly girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.19,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm sure that music box is helping to calm someone else's heart as it calmed mine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.12,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The summer sea, and not a Kumojacky or Kobraja in sight to ruin it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.30,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make this a summer to remember!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I would, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole place is full of lovey-dovey couples!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all those accursed Precures' fault!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'll defeat them, once and for all!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hi there.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.38,0:12:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I have training this afternoon...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be over till late, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.16,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.26,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh... I was running through the mountains recently, and I came across this lavender field.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You like flowers, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you about it, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the same lavender field?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora's?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru, could you show us where it is?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just beyond the pass up ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.99,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the lavender field would be a\N good place to give her back the music box.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really give it back to her, though?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we have here?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! A weirdo!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hrm?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.02,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower of a troubled boy's\N heart. How beautifully it wilts!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Flower of the Heart, come forth!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your cue, Desertrian!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Music box!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.75,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A Desertrian?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.22,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They made him into a Deshertrian!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheeds of the Precure, go forth!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Precure!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Open My Heart!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.17,0:15:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A lone flower, blooming from the earth!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cure Blossom!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A lone flower, swaying in the sea breeze!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cure Marine!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A lone flower, bathing in the Sun's rays!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cure Sunshine!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.12,0:16:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Music box!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunflower Protection!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Music box!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bombs away!{they're shouting "Tamaya" which is the name of an old famous fireworks company in old Japan. It's kind of customary to shout that whenever a firework goes up. I think this is sort of similarly cheeky but if you have a CUSTOMARY AMERICAN THING TO SHOUT DURING FIREWORKS that'd also be cool.} {We don't really have anything like that in Americaland, other than OOOH AHH WOW. So this works.}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.68,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had Hanasaki's music box all this time!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I feel sleepy...{Nobody interrupts my Metal Gear 1 reference. NOBODY.} {HNNNNNNNGGGGGGGGG.}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw something fall out of her car when she was moving, so I picked it up! {Added 'of.}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you ran after us!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.68,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I chased after you to try to give it back, but I just couldn't catch up!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Hanasakiiiiiiiiii!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Blossom!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather, Floral Power!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiny Tambourine!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers, dance for me!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.61,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Precure Gold Forte Burst!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough of the boring chit-chat.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.43,0:18:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fact is, as much as he sits there worrying, he \Ndidn't have the guts to give the music box back.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a useless brat.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not useless!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's through those worries and \Nuncertainties that people mature!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.82,0:18:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Using his heart and making it into a Desertrian is just cruel!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.49,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it up to here with this!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers, shine forth!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.90,0:19:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Precure Pink Forte Wave!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.90,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! I'll defeat you next time, just you watch!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the Flower of his Heart back!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let'sh return him to normal!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally come around?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.82,0:19:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So this must be the lavender field you were talking about, Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.83,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You held onto it for me when it fell \Nout of our car during the move, right? {Added 'of.'}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How did you know? {do -> did}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't sweat the details.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.18,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha.... Hana... saki...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... I...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.28,0:20:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. What did you want to tell me just now?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Forget it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you again, won't I?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you will!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.40,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the language of flowers, lavender means "I'll be waiting for you."
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.52,0:21:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Tsubomi finally \Nrealized Mitsuru's feelings too!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a Heart Seed's about to be born.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.26,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, the Great Heart Tree has recovered a little more!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.06,0:21:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for keeping your promise, Sora.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.23,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really would like to hear you play your cello for me again one day.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.59,0:22:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be waiting for you. {I misted up.}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:09.89,0:22:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:17.98,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,So come on, let's sing together in harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.19,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Come on, all together now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.69,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:32.62,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,When you give life your all, within your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:38.21,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,a shining flower begins to bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:47.18,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,So when you feel like crying, raise your head
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:53.89,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,and you'll see everyone's there by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:59.98,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,So let's dance together, hand in hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:04.36,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,All those
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:08.94,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,happy feelings will be shared amongst us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:14.19,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Lose yourself is the melody!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:16.86,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Yay, yay, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:21.07,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow will bring even more Hallelujahs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:27.21,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,So come on! Let's make the Flowers of our Hearts bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.30,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,With all our might!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:34.59,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:37.76,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,HeartCatch Precure!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:42.06,0:23:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahh! It's over!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you freaking out about?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:45.36,0:23:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Argh, but it just won't end!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:46.78,0:23:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Erika, none of the viewers are gonna \Nhave any clue what you're talking about! {lit: "people in front of the TV."} {on -> talking}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:49.78,0:23:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try to make it at least shound like a preview!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.57,0:23:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer vacation's almost over! But that loathsome beast won't leave me alone! {fixed spelling of loathsome}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing can come from loathing, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:57.52,0:23:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You need love! Love will get you through it!
